name: Leon's Breakfast Dinner
description:
This is a fnaf fangame

Taking place inbetween fnaf 1 and fnaf 3 you play as vannessa put in charge of a location owned by a former fazbear employee. things seem eerie with a smelly crocodile, wierd rooster, this lion and what ever the hell this rabbit is but it's nothing compared when one man's agony awakes
